data.description: Charming remodeled rancher near downtown Huntsville, close to Alabama A&M, UAH, and the Arsenal. This updated home features a modern kitchen, renovated bath, new flooring, and fixtures. Situated on a spacious fenced lot, it offers convenience to shopping, restaurants, and various amenities, making it an ideal residence for those seeking both comfort and proximity to key locations. Newer roof, HVAC 2019.
